黎講)。輕鬆黎講就緊係Full Time啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁做邊隻工種會較易carry到讀書&amp;返工？ 咩公司好？</blockquote><br />\n而家做緊Contractor, 圍內都有1,2個係PT RMIT。聽其他師兄講N展黎講，想輕鬆做維修保養實好過工程，普遍都係整完就走準時收工，不過冇乜特別野學。做工程太多手尾要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n師兄係main con定sub con?<br />\n兼顧到兩邊？ 唔該師兄</blockquote><br />\nSub仔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得都要兼顧到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都係騎牛搵馬(我指HD仔) U grad就慘啲，行Scheme兩年走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽返黎都話Scheme 係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084de9cd9b2d770f2a6aa0e2ccbb4fc55e5840fe","tid":315113,"uid":47812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我就做住先再加PT，始終做工程都係睇經驗多，搵工時好多都係要求hd加2年經驗/U FG ，論U grad，RMIT 又唔夠8大比(我估香港HR睇法)。所以倒不如PT仲好(錢途黎講)。輕鬆黎講就緊係Full Time啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁做邊隻工種會較易carry到讀書&amp;返工？ 咩公司好？</blockquote><br />\n而家做緊Contractor, 圍內都有1,2個係PT RMIT。聽其他師兄講N展黎講，想輕鬆做維修保養實好過工程，普遍都係整完就走準時收工，不過冇乜特別野學。做工程太多手尾要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n師兄係main con定sub con?<br />\n兼顧到兩邊？ 唔該師兄</blockquote><br />\nSub仔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得都要兼顧到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都係騎牛搵馬(我指HD仔) U grad就慘啲，行Scheme兩年走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽返黎都話Scheme 係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網睇，我見scheme 好似係好野，快chartered 到？"},{"pid":"49fd5c2054ec8d19dc07fae4a81371a9d307c1e1","tid":315113,"uid":47812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"如果入consultant公司做ae 再讀p